content.markdown:
## First Stage Fuels

First stage fuels include boosters + main rocket. {launch_count} launches by {rockets} rockets. Average ISP {average_isp}. Note that the payload over time chart below totals will duplicate payload for a launch if it had multiple upper stage fuel types. 

### Top 3 Fuels in Filter Set
{{#each fuel_payloads limit=3}}
- {fuel}: {payload} tonnes to orbit (Success rate: {success_rate}%)
{{/each}}

content.query:
import std.display;
WHERE
    vehicle.stage_no in ('0', '1')
SELECT
    launch_count,
    sum(orb_pay) as payload_to_orbit,
    count(vehicle.full_name) as rockets,
    round(avg(group(vehicle.stage.engine.isp) by flight_id),2) -> average_isp,
    array_sort(array_agg(
        struct(
        round(coalesce(sum(orb_pay) by vehicle.stage.engine.fuel,0),3)  ->payload , 
        vehicle.stage.engine.fuel  ->fuel,
        @calc_percent(
            (count(launch_tag ? was_complete_success ) by vehicle.stage.engine.fuel), 
            (count(launch_tag) by vehicle.stage.engine.fuel)
            , 2
         )*100 ->success_rate 

         )
    ), desc) as fuel_payloads
;

